
## Home Lab — Security Practice Environment

A personal lab built to simulate enterprise environments and practice offensive/defensive techniques hands-on.

**Infrastructure**
- Proxmox hypervisor hosting a Windows Server 2016 Active Directory domain, Windows 10 clients, and an air-gapped endpoint for malware analysis
- Dedicated attack platform(laptop) running Parrot OS against intentionally vulnerable targets (VulnHub)

**Practice areas**
- Active Directory enumeration, lateral movement, privilege escalation
- Red team vs blue team exercises on isolated networks
- Vulnerability exploitation and post-exploitation techniques
- Web app vunerabilities
